Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation This package contains classes which support BPEL validation.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity This package contains implementation classes for activity validation models. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.assign This package contains validation model classes for validating the assign activity. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.decision This package contains validation model implementation classes for if, elseif, and else constructs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.links This package contains implementation classes for link-related validation models (such as source, target, link, etc...). 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.scope This package contains validation model implementation classes for scope related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.wsio This package contains validation model implementation classes for WSIO related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr This package contains classes which support validation of expressions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr.xpath This package contains classes which support validation of expressions written in the xpath language. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expressions This package contains validation model implementation classes for expression based validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.extensions This package contains validation model implementation classes for extensions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.process   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.variable This package contains validation model implementation classes for validating variables. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.validation.javascript This package contains classes which support validation of expressions written in the javascript language. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.validation.xquery This package contains classes which support validation of expressions written in the xquery language. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy Process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Deployment Validation code.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate.main Root package for running the pre-deployment validation code in stand alone mode. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.logging In-memory and persistent logging facilities.
